---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="App Vitals — AI Adoption for Engineering Teams">
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 pt-24 pb-20 md:pt-32 md:pb-28">
    <div class="max-w-3xl">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-bold leading-[1.1] tracking-tight">
        Ship faster with AI.<br />
        <span class="text-electric-500">Without lowering your standards.</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="mt-6 text-lg md:text-xl text-gray-400 max-w-2xl leading-relaxed">
        We embed with your engineering team to build AI adoption practices that spread organically and compound over time. No mandates. No compliance theater. No shortcuts.
      </p>
      <div class="mt-8 flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4">
        <a
          href="https://cal.com/app-vitals/discovery"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-3 bg-electric-500 hover:bg-electric-600 rounded-lg text-lg font-medium transition-colors"
        >
          Book a Discovery Call
        </a>
        <a
          href="/about"
          class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-3 border border-white/20 hover:border-white/40 rounded-lg text-lg font-medium transition-colors text-gray-300 hover:text-white"
        >
          Learn More
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Social Proof -->
  <section class="border-y border-white/10 bg-navy-800/50">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 py-10 text-center">
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-400 uppercase tracking-widest mb-1">
        40+ years combined experience at
      </p>
      <p class="text-lg text-gray-300 font-medium">
        Uber · Alto Pharmacy · Enterprise Partners
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Value Props -->
  <section class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 py-20 md:py-28">
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight">
        What makes us different
      </h2>
      <p class="mt-4 text-gray-400 text-lg max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Most AI consultants roll out tools. We build the practices and infrastructure that make those tools actually useful.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
      <div class="p-8 rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-navy-800/30 hover:border-electric-500/30 transition-colors">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-electric-500/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-electric-500" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M17 20h5v-2a3 3 0 00-5.356-1.857M17 20H7m10 0v-2c0-.656-.126-1.283-.356-1.857M7 20H2v-2a3 3 0 015.356-1.857M7 20v-2c0-.656.126-1.283.356-1.857m0 0a5.002 5.002 0 019.288 0M15 7a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zm6 3a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0zM7 10a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">Champion Enablement</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
          We find your early adopters and coach them into AI champions who teach the rest of the team. Bottom-up adoption that sticks — not top-down mandates that get ignored.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="p-8 rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-navy-800/30 hover:border-electric-500/30 transition-colors">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-electric-500/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-electric-500" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M19.428 15.428a2 2 0 00-1.022-.547l-2.387-.477a6 6 0 00-3.86.517l-.318.158a6 6 0 01-3.86.517L6.05 15.21a2 2 0 00-1.806.547M8 4h8l-1 1v5.172a2 2 0 00.586 1.414l5 5c1.26 1.26.367 3.414-1.415 3.414H4.828c-1.782 0-2.674-2.154-1.414-3.414l5-5A2 2 0 009 10.172V5L8 4z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">Context Infrastructure</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
          AI tools are only as good as the context they have. We build the foundation — architecture docs, shared patterns, security safeguards — that makes AI actually understand your codebase.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="p-8 rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-navy-800/30 hover:border-electric-500/30 transition-colors">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-electric-500/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-electric-500" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">Week 1 Delivery</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
          We ship production code by Friday, not PowerPoints. Most consultants spend Week 1 in meetings. We spend it generating architecture docs, building dashboards, and identifying champions.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- How We Work -->
  <section class="border-y border-white/10 bg-navy-800/20">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 py-20 md:py-28">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight">
          How we work
        </h2>
        <p class="mt-4 text-gray-400 text-lg max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          A focused 6-week pilot that proves the model — then scales.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <div class="relative">
          <div class="text-electric-500 text-sm font-mono font-bold mb-3">WEEKS 1–2</div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">Identify Champions</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
            Meet 3–5 engineers on your team. Identify 1–3 early adopters who are already excited about AI. These become your internal champions.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="relative">
          <div class="text-electric-500 text-sm font-mono font-bold mb-3">WEEKS 3–4</div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">Create Quick Wins</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
            Pair with champions on real work. Ship to production. Demo to the team. Build the evidence that AI adoption works — with your code, your standards, your processes.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="relative">
          <div class="text-electric-500 text-sm font-mono font-bold mb-3">WEEKS 5–6</div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">Enable Evangelism</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
            Champions start teaching others. You support from the background. By Week 6, adoption is spreading organically — without you in the room.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Results -->
  <section class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 py-20 md:py-28">
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight">
        The outcome
      </h2>
    </div>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 text-center">
      <div>
        <div class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-electric-500 mb-2">2–3×</div>
        <p class="text-gray-400">Faster shipping velocity</p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <div class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-electric-500 mb-2">6 weeks</div>
        <p class="text-gray-400">To organic adoption</p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <div class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-electric-500 mb-2">0</div>
        <p class="text-gray-400">Standards compromised</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-16 p-8 rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-navy-800/30 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <blockquote class="text-lg text-gray-300 leading-relaxed italic">
        "Same bar for AI code as human code. You're responsible, not the tool."
      </blockquote>
      <p class="mt-4 text-sm text-gray-500">— Our philosophy on AI adoption</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Final CTA -->
  <section class="border-t border-white/10 bg-navy-800/20">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 py-20 md:py-28 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight">
        Your team should be moving faster.
      </h2>
      <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-gray-400 max-w-xl mx-auto">
        Book a 30-minute discovery call. We'll talk about where your team is, where it should be, and whether we can help.
      </p>
      <a
        href="https://cal.com/app-vitals/discovery"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
        class="inline-flex items-center justify-center mt-8 px-8 py-3 bg-electric-500 hover:bg-electric-600 rounded-lg text-lg font-medium transition-colors"
      >
        Book a Discovery Call
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
